{"word":"G1982 - ἐπισκιάζω - episkiázō - ep-ee-skee-ad'-zo - Overshadow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπισκιάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">episkiázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-skee-ad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Overshadow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிழலிடு"},{"paragraph":"to throw a shadow upon, to envelop in shadow, to overshadow"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4639 - σκιά - skiá - skee'-ah/4639\">G4639</a>; to <i>cast a shade upon</i>, that is, (by analogy) to <i>envelop</i> in a haze of brilliancy; figuratively to <i>invest</i> with preternatural influence: - overshadow.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1982/1982\">G1982</a>, <a href=\"#/G4639/4639\">G4639</a>, <a href=\"#/G644/644\">G644</a>"}]}